cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper presents a new approach to logistic regression that addresses the issue of mislabeling in datasets. This is a common problem in machine learning, particularly in natural language processing tasks such as named entity recognition, which is used as an example in the paper. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
